.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, funk, rock, gospel, blues, soul, dubstep
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening, hiking, rock-climbing, singing, skydiving
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the fan of funk##7
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the fan of gospel##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 5. the fan of electronic is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is chess##7
 6. the fan of soul is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
 7. the fan of blues is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of funk##7
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the fan of blues##5
10. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
11. the person who's hobby is singing is not the fan of dubstep##6
12. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the fan of gospel##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Music-Genre    | dubstep  | rock | soul | gospel | electronic     | blues | funk  |
| Hobby   | gardening | singing | chess  | skydiving  | rock-climbing | hiking      | camping |

