.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: martial-arts, thriller, scientific, superhero, zombie, romance, horror
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, country, d&b, hip-hop, jazz, metal
 1. the fan of metal is between the person watching scientific movies and the fan of country##2
 2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 3. the fan of blues is not the person watching superhero movies##6
 4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 5. the fan of ambient is between the fan of jazz and the person watching zombie movies##2
 6. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 9. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of metal##7
10. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
11. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4
12. the person watching zombie movies is not the fan of ambient##6
13. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching zombie movies##7
14. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
15. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
16. the person watching zombie movies is not the fan of jazz##6
17. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
18. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
19. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |    4    |       5       |     6     |      7      |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts | thriller | romance | zombie  | scientific | superhero | horror |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | jazz       | ambient   | hip-hop | d&b           | metal     | country     |

