 3. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person eating plum##5
 5. the person who's sport is lettuceing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 6. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the person eating cherry is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating kale##7
 8. the person who's sport is lettuceing is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
10. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
11. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
12. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
13. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating apple##1
14. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
16. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person eating cherry##5
17. the person eating lettuce is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person eating plum##2
18. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person eating papaya##6
