 9. the italian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
10. the person driving the train is on the left of the indonesian##1
11. the american is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
12. the american is on the left or right of the japanese##3
13. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the italian and the person driving the quad-bike##7
14. the indonesian is the person driving the helicopter##1
15. the person driving the train is the pakistani##1
16. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
17. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
18. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

